\p
\v 1 Then Yahweh¦68384 told Mosheh¦68387 \add (Moses¦68387)\add*,
\v 2 “Send some men in¦68414 to explore Kanaan—the land that I'm giving to the \add ≈Israelis¦68403\add*. Send one man from each \add ≈ancestral¦68410\add* tribe—a leader¦68413 within that tribe.”
\v 3 Then¦68416 \add ≈at Yahweh's command\add*, Mosheh¦68418 sent¦68416 them off from the Paran¦68420 wilderness¦68419. They were all \add ≈Israeli¦68428\add* leaders
\v 4 and¦68433 their¦68434 names¦68434 were:
\li1 Shammua¦68437 (Zakkur's son) from Reuven tribe¦68435,
\li1
