\v 41 \add ≈The next\add* morning¦74414, Balak¦74416 took¦74415 Bileam uphill to Bamot¦74421-Baal¦74422, and¦74413 from there¦74424 \add @they\add* could see the outskirts¦74425 of the \add ≈Israeli camp\add*.
\c 23
\s1 Bileam blesses Yisrael
