\q1 ≈\add ≡Who can even\add* count a quarter of the \add ≈Israelis¦74580\add*?
\q1 Let me die¦74582 like \add those\add* honourable \add >people\add*,
\q1 ≈and let my end¦74587 be like \add #theirs\add*.”
