\v 11 \add ≈But¦74590\add* Balak¦74591 \add ≈demanded from\add* Bileam, “What have you done to me? I brought¦74600 you \add here\add* to curse¦74598 my enemies¦74599, and¦74590 \add ≈blast it all\add*—you've¦74602 actually¦74603 blessed¦74602 \add <them\add*!”
\p
\v 12 “Shouldn't I be careful to \add only\add* say \add ≈what Yahweh¦74611 tells me\add*?” Bileam \add ≈answered¦74605 back\add*.
