\v 21 \add @Yahweh¦74749\add* hasn't \add ≈considered\add* hardship for Yakov \add (Jacob)\add*,
\q1 ≈and he hasn't seen¦74746 trouble¦74747 for Yisrael¦74748 \add (Israel¦74748)\add*.
