\p
\v 27 Then¦74833 \add King\add* Balak¦74834 told Bileam, “Come \add ≈with me\add*. I'll take¦74841 you to another¦74845 place¦74844. Perhaps it will \add ≈pleased¦74840\add* God \add ≈if\add* you curse¦74850 \add #them\add* for me from there¦74852.”
\v 28 \add ≈So¦74854\add* Balak¦74855 took¦74854 \add *him\add* to the top of \add Mt¦74858.\add* Peor¦74860 \add ≈that¦74861 faces down\add* to the wilderness,
